text: The Internazionali di Tenis Femminili Città di Latina was a tournament for professional female tennis players played on outdoor clay courts. The event was classified as a $50,000 ITF Women's Circuit tournament and was held in Latina, Italy, in 2003 and from 2007 to 2009.
